      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "Siding with AUTUMNHEAT (1) first up. He's off a decent spell here but his form last time in reads well for this level, fourth at Flemington, a BM66 winner at Geelong, second to the very progressive Straand Deal just some of the highlights. This trip is on the short side but he draws well and might just have a class edge. AMPHACTOR (5) has had three runs back and been solid enough in all, good at Geelong last time when third. He'll get a nice run and take catching. SAVVIE BLANC (4) was just fair fresh when fifth over 1400m here last start. Better for that run and can improve. ZESHADOW (8) was in the money two starts back at Pakenham Synthetic but couldn't back that up when unplaced over 1600m at Sandown-Lakeside last time. Can bounce back.",
